                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6869" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1074</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7986 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国际期货逼空事件：青山镍险象环生</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">International futures short-selling incident: Qingshan nickel is full of dangers</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨锋，罗港</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国科学技术大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">青山控股集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钢铁行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">镍期货；期货逼空事件；金融衍生品；交易所修改规则</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Nickel futures; Futures short-selling event; Financial derivatives; Exchange modification rules</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022年3月，随着俄乌局势的变化，镍资源的交易受到了限制。短短两日，伦敦金属交易所的镍期货价格暴涨三倍多。手持大量镍期货空单的青山集团惨遭“逼空”，面临爆仓风险。在此极端行情下，伦敦金属交易所紧急发布公告，宣布修改交易规则。青山集团争取到了喘息的时间，立即采取应对措施，险象环生，化险为夷，最终逃过此劫。本案例以国际形势和资源布局为背景，讲述了青山集团在国际期货市场上遭遇海外资本围剿的事件始末，具体论述了引发此次事件的原因和衍生品市场上各方举措的动因。本案例使读者在学习期货产品的特征、期货交易市场的交易制度、衍生品市场在企业运作中的作用等知识点的基础之上，引发其对实体企业在金融市场上寻求避险的同时如何能够避免金融市场带来的次生风险的思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In March 2022, as the situation in Russia and Ukraine changed, the trading of nickel resources was restricted. In just two days, nickel futures prices on the London Metal Exchange have more than tripled. Qingshan Group, which holds a large number of nickel futures short orders, was tragically &quot;forced to short&quot; and faced the risk of blowing up. Under this extreme market, the London Metal Exchange issued an urgent announcement announcing changes to the trading rules. The Qingshan Group gained respite, and eventually the danger arose. Taking the international situation and resource layout as the background, this case tells the beginning and end of the incident in which Qingshan Group encountered overseas capital in the international futures market, and specifically discusses the reasons for this incident and the motivation of various measures in the derivatives market. This case enables the reader to learn the characteristics of futures products, the trading system of the futures trading market, the role of the derivatives market in the operation of enterprises and other knowledge points, and triggers their thinking on how entities can avoid the secondary risks brought by the financial market while seeking hedging in the financial market.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《金融衍生工具》、《金融风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">期货的基本概念；金融衍生工具的经济功能；期、现货溢价理论；供求均衡理论；期货市场的基本制度；期货多、空头属性；金融衍生产品的风险管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
